{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/museum-ninja-hattori-kampung-halaman-pencipta-ninja-hattori-kini-jadi-pusat-wisata/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"[Museum Ninja Hattori] Kampung Halaman Pencipta Ninja Hattori Kini Jadi Pusat Wisata!","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bro sis tahu dong Doraemon? Ikon pop culture Jepang yang sudah dikenal di seluruh dunia. Kucing robot dari abad ke-22 itu merupakan karakter manga dan anime Jepang yang dikenal serta dicintai begitu banyak orang dari berbagai jenis usia dan bangsa. Diciptakan oleh seniman manga Fujiko Fujio sejak 1969, Doraemon tetap memiliki fanbase yang sangat banyak hingga hari ini.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41382\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41382\" data-attachment-id=\"41382\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/museum-ninja-hattori-kampung-halaman-pencipta-ninja-hattori-kini-jadi-pusat-wisata/attachment/hatori1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Doraemon. Sumber gambar: epic-rap-battles-of-cartoons.wikia.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Doraemon. Sumber gambar: epic-rap-battles-of-cartoons.wikia.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41382 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori1.jpg\" alt=\"Doraemon. Sumber gambar: epic-rap-battles-of-cartoons.wikia.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41382\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Doraemon. Sumber gambar: epic-rap-battles-of-cartoons.wikia.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tapi tahukan bro sis, kalau “Fujiko Fujio” ini adalah sebuah team? Two-man team?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fujiko Fujio adalah duo mangaka yang terdiri dari dua sosok. “Fujiko F. Fujio” memiliki nama asli Fujimoto Hiroshi 藤本 弘 , sementara “Fujiko Fujio A” adalah nama pena untuk Abiko Motoo 安孫子 素雄 . Kedua mangaka ini menciptakan banyak cerita dan karakter dalam perjalanan karir mereka. Karena berupa team, maka banyak persepsi keliru yang mengiringi karya mereka. Saya termasuk yang bingung mengenai hal ini sebelumnya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41384\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41384\" data-attachment-id=\"41384\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/museum-ninja-hattori-kampung-halaman-pencipta-ninja-hattori-kini-jadi-pusat-wisata/attachment/hatori2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fujimoto Hiroshi, Doraemon &#038; Abiko Motoo. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/phoenix_ag\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Fujimoto Hiroshi, Doraemon &#038; Abiko Motoo. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/phoenix_ag&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori2.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41384 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori2.jpg\" alt=\"Fujimoto Hiroshi, Doraemon &amp; Abiko Motoo. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/phoenix_ag\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41384\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fujimoto Hiroshi, Doraemon &amp; Abiko Motoo. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/phoenix_ag</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Doraemon adalah karya dari Fujimoto Hiroshi dengan nama pena Fujiko F. Fujio. Fujimoto tidak hanya menciptakan Doraemon. Dia juga membuat Mojacko, Pokonyan! , Esper Mami, dan masih banyak lagi.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sementara Fujiko Fujio A, atau Abiko Motoo, menciptakan karakter seperti Ninja Hattori-kun, Kaibutsu-kun, Miss Dracula dan beberapa lainnya.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Apa mereka punya karya hasil kolaborasi bersama? Tidak banyak. Tercatat hanya ada dua judul, yaitu UTOPIA the Final World War 最後の世界大戦 (1953) dan Obake no Q-taro オバケのQ太郎 (1964-1966, 1971-1974).</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41385\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41385\" data-attachment-id=\"41385\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/museum-ninja-hattori-kampung-halaman-pencipta-ninja-hattori-kini-jadi-pusat-wisata/attachment/hatori3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Obake no Q-taro. Sumber gambar: gamefaqs.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Obake no Q-taro. Sumber gambar: gamefaqs.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori3.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41385 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori3.jpg\" alt=\"Obake no Q-taro. Sumber gambar: gamefaqs.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41385\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Obake no Q-taro. Sumber gambar: gamefaqs.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jadi mangaka “Fujiko Fujio” adalah sebuah team yang terdiri dari dua orang berbeda dan menghasilkan karya-karya yang berbeda pula (walau punya kesamaan dan kemiripan antara satu dengan yang lainnya). Hal ini perlu diketahui agar tidak kebingungan saat membedakan karya-karya yang dihasilkan di bawah bendera “Fujiko Fujio Production”.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pencipta Doraemon, atau Fujimoto Hiroshi, kini sudah wafat tahun 1996 di usia 62 tahun. Sementara kreator Ninja Hattori-kun, Abiko Motoo, masih hidup dan kini berusia 83 tahun.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41386\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41386\" data-attachment-id=\"41386\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/museum-ninja-hattori-kampung-halaman-pencipta-ninja-hattori-kini-jadi-pusat-wisata/attachment/hatori4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fujimoto Hiroshi. Sumber gambar: akibatan.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Fujimoto Hiroshi. Sumber gambar: akibatan.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori4.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41386 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori4.jpg\" alt=\"Fujimoto Hiroshi. Sumber gambar: akibatan.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41386\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fujimoto Hiroshi. Sumber gambar: akibatan.com</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_41387\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41387\" data-attachment-id=\"41387\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/museum-ninja-hattori-kampung-halaman-pencipta-ninja-hattori-kini-jadi-pusat-wisata/attachment/hatori5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Abiko Motoo. Sumber gamba: acg.92wy.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Abiko Motoo. Sumber gamba: acg.92wy.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori5.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41387 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori5.jpg\" alt=\"Abiko Motoo. Sumber gamba: acg.92wy.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41387\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Abiko Motoo. Sumber gamba: acg.92wy.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ninja Hattori termasuk karya fenomenal dari Fujiko Fujio, dan kota kelahiran Abiko mengapresiasi karya warganya tersebut dalam bentuk <em>‘tribute’</em>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kota Himi di prefektur Toyama adalah tempat kelahiran dari Abiko. Kota ini kini dikenal sebagai “Fujiko Fujio A Manga World”, dimana berbagai hal yang mewakili karya-karya Fujiko Fujio yang berasal dari Abiko dipamerkan disini sebagai bagian atraksi turisme.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Seperti misalnya patung karakter manga Kaibutsu-kun yang didirikan di depan kuil Kozenji di distrik Marunouchi yang menyambut pengunjung di pintu depan kuil. Di dalam kuil terdapat pula “Moguro Daruma” yang digambar oleh Abiko. Abiko sendiri lahir di kuil ini. Kepala kuil Kozenji, Koichi Kikuchi (yang juga merupakan keponakan Abiko Motoo) mengatakan kalau dia meminta pamannya itu untuk menggambar sesuatu sebagai bukti / untuk menunjukkan pada pengunjung kalau Abiko merupakan bagian dari kuil ini. Abiko sendiri adalah anak kepala kuil Kozenji pada tahun 1934. Seharusnya Abiko meneruskan profesi ayahnya sebagai kepala kuil, namun nasib membawa dia ke bidang seni saat bertemu dengan Hiroshi Fujimoto di kota tetangga, Takaoka.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41388\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41388\" data-attachment-id=\"41388\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/museum-ninja-hattori-kampung-halaman-pencipta-ninja-hattori-kini-jadi-pusat-wisata/attachment/hatori6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kozenji Temple. Sumber gambar: tripadvisor.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kozenji Temple. Sumber gambar: tripadvisor.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori6.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41388 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori6.jpg\" alt=\"Kozenji Temple. Sumber gambar: tripadvisor.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41388\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kozenji Temple. Sumber gambar: tripadvisor.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Di tahun 1992, pemerintah kota membangun jam dengan patung-patung karakter Ninja Hattori di atas jembatan sungai Minatogawa yang berada di dekat distrik pusat perbelanjaan dan menamai jembatan tersebut sebagai “Niji no Hashi” alias jembatan pelangi.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41389\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41389\" data-attachment-id=\"41389\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/museum-ninja-hattori-kampung-halaman-pencipta-ninja-hattori-kini-jadi-pusat-wisata/attachment/hatori7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/hatori7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Niji no Hashi, Himi Machi, Toyama. Su